  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Control the non-blocking state of the given file descriptor,
according to <code>nonblock</code>. On most systems this uses %O_NONBLOCK, but
on some older ones may use %O_NDELAY.</p>
  <p>Since 2.30</p>
